{"type": "article", "id": 23606, "title": "像钨丝一样的灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-10T07:30:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110756PA1c46njtEQwpF9m.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏灯就像一个放大的钨丝圈，来自乌克兰的年轻设计师 Michael Samoriz。实际上灯泡的一段在最下面，上面大部分都是灯管，从侧面看就是一个渐渐缩小的圆环，体现出极简现代的特征。悬挂这盏灯的线很长，让它可以适合餐厅、酒吧等环境。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110753aAwimFrd4hXf8tcp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110754YLx4pfMmw1hN8T93.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110754nR9ocqXZyusPN57p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021107555MOrvg1fRkAqtGEp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}